28\/hamd-eating-drinking\/","url_meta":{"origin":18840,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Gratitude: Praise Allah for food and drink","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is pleased with a servant who praises Him when he eats, or praises Him when he drinks.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2734 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34088,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/01\/believers-praise-even-in-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":18840,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hamd: Believers praise Allah even as they die","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 1, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the believer is in good shape in every situation. He praises Allah Almighty even while his soul is taken out of his body.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2475 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":""